name: Hein. Surf & Skate Muscle Tee
description: It's nearly festival season, and what better kit to wear than a good ol' muscle tee? Sporting the brand spanking new "Hein. Surf & Skate" logo, this tee will work a treat in any situation. Whether you're chilling at the beach, partying hard at a music festival, or attending your' mates wedding, this tee will make a great staple in your wardrobe this summer!

name: Heinous Goods Logo
description:
The "Heinous Goods Logo" design is a Heinous Goods original, and is one of the first designs featured in the 2013/2014 Summer range. The simplicity of the shirt makes for a great base to go with basically any outfit, making for a great summer shirt. The shirt features the Heinous Goods logo on the left pectoral. 

All designs are printed on high quality and very durable shirts, which are 180gsm in weight and 100% Pre-Shrunk Cotton which make for a quality durable shirt.

This shirt will be available November, though contact me for any pre-orders (Including size and shirt) and and get your name in quick for a reserve. Also contact me for any information regarding shirts, shipping etc.
